analysis.name: UC-Maps
analysis.description: Developed a mobile application to map the University of Cincinnati campus.
achievements: Successfully created a cross-platform mobile application with intuitive navigation for both iOS and Android.
Implemented a scalable architecture that allows for future feature additions and updates.
Managed the entire project lifecycle, from initial design to deployment, ensuring consistent progress and quality.
key_features: Interactive campus map with user-friendly interface.
Utilized Dart and Flutter for cross-platform application development.
Designed and implemented the application using consistent software engineering principles.
